1
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:08,320
If anything happens once we're inside,

2
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,600
stick close to him.

3
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,760
He'll make a perfect human shield.

4
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:12,480
Got it.

5
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:14,360
Bro.

6
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,880
I'm counting on you in there.

7
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:22,200
How did I give birth to a piece of trash like you?

8
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:24,720
Enough.

9
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,400
I came to apologize, didn't I?

10
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,400
Look at the idiot you raised.

11
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,640
I'm not an idiot.

12
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,560
If it weren't for him,

13
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,240
would those two old bastards downstairs

14
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,560
be haunting us like this?

15
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:35,440
Is he just my son?

16
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:37,600
He learned all this from you.

17
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,600
From me?

18
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,480
If he learned from me, he wouldn't be mixed up

19
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,000
in all this superstitious nonsense.

20
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,000
Master Wang said you'd be in trouble,

21
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,160
and sure enough, you got into a car crash.

22
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,600
If you're not scared, don't come then!

23
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,240
Say that again.

24
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,520
It's just me and my son anyway.

25
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,240
Ma'am.

26
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,160
Over here, over here.

27
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,960
Welcome, everyone.

28
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,160
Where's Master Wang?

29
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,720
He promised me

30
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,440
that once today's matter is settled,

31
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,200
our house

32
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,000
will definitely sell at market price.

33
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,560
Yes, it'll definitely sell.

34
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,240
My master must have told you already.

35
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:10,320
You need to show some respect.

36
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,040
When it's time to apologize,

37
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,400
you apologize.

38
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,600
What do you mean?

39
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,360
Are you threatening us?

40
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:24,240
If you don't mind being haunted forever,

41
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,400
constant arguments,

42
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,480
nothing going right,

43
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,320
then forget I said anything.

44
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,000
But

45
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,680
you've got a child at home, too.

46
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,000
I can see that thing.

47
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,240
It's the auntie from downstairs.

48
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:43,560
Son.

49
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,240
What nonsense are you talking?

50
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,800
Don't scare Mommy.

51
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:49,000
She's following you, Daddy.

52
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:56,880
Scared now, aren't you?

53
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,400
Just spouting nonsense, huh?

54
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,680
What are you doing?

55
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,320
Let go!

56
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:07,720
Still want to solve this?

57
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,120
Coward.

58
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,000
Let's go.

59
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,400
That kid

60
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,160
can see it, too.

61
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,800
We'll find out once we go up.

62
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,320
Let's go.

63
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,600
Zhou Yi, what's going on?

64
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,680
It's definitely fake.

65
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,080
We just need him to put on a show.

66
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,680
On the Stone of Three Lives,

67
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,640
the Five Elements turn!

68
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,240
Spirits descend,

69
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,240
realms become one!

70
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,720
The path to the underworld

71
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,640
opens!

72
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,200
Evil spirits, come forth

73
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,600
and heed my command!

74
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,960
Can you really

75
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:30,160
summon my daughter back?

76
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:32,440
Is she still here right now?

77
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,400
Sir,

78
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:39,560
Ma'am,

79
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,400
no matter what happens next,

80
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,680
please stay calm.

81
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,760
The Li family came here today to apologize.

82
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:47,160
They should know what they did was wrong.

83
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,120
The dead are gone.

84
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,160
We came here today

85
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:49,840
just to

86
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,120
help you both find closure.

87
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,640
By the decree of the Founding Master,

88
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,520
I humbly summon Immortal Taiyi!

89
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,040
With this talisman as proof,

90
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:02,760
with this incense as guide,

91
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,960
spirit of Yiyi,

92
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,760
descend at once!

93
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:07,960
Come.

94
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,720
Kneel.

95
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,600
What are you doing?

96
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,160
Are you trying to get me killed?

97
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,640
Why should I kneel?

98
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:40,080
I'm not the one who killed her.

99
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,120
You said it yourself: survival of the fittest.

100
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,040
She was weak, she deserved it.

101
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,720
She was wasting national resources.

102
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,600
What are you saying?

103
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,320
Hey, what are you doing?

104
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,240
Yell over there.

105
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,560
What's going on?

106
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,640
Don't take it out on the kid!

107
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,960
And wasn't the one you hurt

108
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,160
somebody else's child too?

109
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,320
Fine then.

110
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,440
Let him see.

111
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,800
Teach him a lesson.

112
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,360
Go check on your son.

113
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,240
Son!

114
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,880
Son, what's wrong?

115
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,160
Say something!

116
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,280
Son, are you okay?

117
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,040
Talk to me!

118
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,760
Son!

119
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,160
Son!

120
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,280
He's fine.

121
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:30,000
He actually just saw the auntie from downstairs.

122
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,400
On Qingming and the 15th,

123
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,480
remember to burn incense and offerings for Yiyi.

124
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,600
Whatever compensation the old couple deserves,

125
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,240
give it all to them. It's okay, dear.

126
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,480
Once Yiyi rests in peace,

127
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,920
your son will naturally be fine too.

128
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:42,680
Fine.

129
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,680
But if he keeps acting like this,

130
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,200
I can't guarantee

131
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,640
whether he'll run into

132
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,040
something else later on.

133
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,120
Son!

134
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,280
My dad's the one who killed you.

135
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,080
It wasn't me.

136
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,280
Son, I didn't do it.

137
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,760
Son, what's wrong? I didn't kill you!

138
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,960
It wasn't me! It wasn't me!

139
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,120
Son!

140
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,880
That's enough.

141
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,000
Don't...

142
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,080
Too late.

143
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:26,800
Zhou Yi.

144
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,680
Zhou Yi!

145
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,600
She's not Zhou Yi.

146
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,800
Your yang energy is too strong.

147
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,960
You might end up hurting her.

148
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,120
Then...

149
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,360
What do we do?

150
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,760
I'll try to communicate with her first.

151
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,520
If she loses control,

152
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,360
then you step in.

153
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,120
No way.

154
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,800
Didn't you say I have a strong destiny?

155
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,240
Let me try.

156
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,800
Fine, we'll die together.

157
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,320
My girl.

158
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,680
My girl.

159
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,080
It's Mom.

160
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,040
Look at Mom.

161
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,800
Mom misses you so much.

162
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,440
Mom.

163
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:14,880
Dad.

164
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,240
I'm sorry.

165
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,680
I broke your hearts.

166
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,920
I've been an unworthy daughter.

167
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,640
I want to come home.

168
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:25,000
I want to be with you.

169
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,480
But I can't find my way home.

170
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,120
Mom.

171
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,440
Dad.

172
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,440
My darling girl.

173
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:35,720
Dad failed you.

174
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,080
Please forgive Dad.

175
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,919
Dad didn't protect you.

176
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,200
I'm sorry.

177
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,120
I'm the one who should've died.

178
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:52,320
I'm so sorry, my girl.

179
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,200
It's all my fault.

180
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,400
Yiyi is already gone.

181
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,040
What's the use of saying this now?

182
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,320
She wouldn't want to see

183
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,520
you like this.

184
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,160
She keeps saying she's sorry.

185
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,920
She just doesn't want you to grieve.

186
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:12,040
She only wants to say a proper goodbye.

187
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,840
She doesn't hate anyone.

188
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:18,320
She just can't bear to leave you.

189
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,400
My girl.

190
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,400
Dad is so sorry.

191
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,840
Your dad...

192
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,880
didn't take care of you and Mom.

193
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:38,440
I brought you into this world just to suffer.

194
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,240
If there's a next life,

195
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,240
Dad hopes you'll

196
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,840
choose a good family

197
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,840
and live a wonderful life.

198
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:52,480
My girl.

199
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,440
Mom and Dad

200
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:58,080
will love you forever.

201
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,320
Time's almost up.

202
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:11,400
It could hurt Zhou Yi.

203
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,880
What are you doing?

204
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,400
The living and the dead walk separate paths.

205
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,120
Your attachment

206
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,120
will only bind Yiyi's soul.

207
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:30,720
Burn it.

208
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,160
Only when you let go

209
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,720
can she truly be free.

210
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:57,440
Dad.

211
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,120
Mom.

212
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,160
Take care of yourselves.

213
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,360
I'm leaving now.

214
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,920
Go home if you want to lie down.

215
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:26,760
Playing the daughter and the Taoist...

216
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,040
It's exhausting.

217
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,160
Still got that medicine from old Wang?

218
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:36,120
Go home, take a shower,

219
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:37,640
and get some proper rest.

220
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,600
Just let me lie here a while.

221
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:44,680
If my sis finds out I'm mixed up with Daji,

222
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,520
she'll nag me to death again.

223
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,600
Sister Yaoyao.

224
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,760
Help me, Sister Yaoyao!

225
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:03,560
My savior!

226
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:04,640
You promised to have my back.

227
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:08,840
Who said they'd handle trouble themselves?

228
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:10,720
It's for you.

229
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,200
Hello?

230
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:17,960
Sis, it's Zhou Yi.

231
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,640
Where the hell have you been, you brat?

232
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,760
Meddling in someone else's mess again?

233
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,880
No, sis.

234
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,280
Get your butt back here right now!

235
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:26,160
No, stop yelling, sis.

236
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,280
Don't yell, don't yell.

237
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:29,280
Let me explain. It's not...

238
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:40,480
Is Zhou Yi okay?

239
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:44,160
He really swapped places with Yiyi?

240
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,240
Weren't you helping Yiyi earlier,

241
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,400
cursing out her dad?

242
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,000
I thought

243
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,680
you could actually see her.

244
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:55,320
Well, I...

245
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,760
I was just getting emotional.

246
00:12:58,640 --> 00:12:59,640
But I think that girl

247
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:01,160
must've felt the same way.

248
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,640
Work on your courage first.

249
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,600
Here, take this back.

250
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:20,120
Consider it a reward

251
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,040
for finishing the job.

252
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,200
So...

253
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,760
am I officially in now?

254
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:33,880
What do you think?
